Features :
  1. Secure Login using PIN-based authentication

  2. Generate PIN for new users

  3. Withdraw and Deposit money

  4. Change PIN securely

  5.Check Balance functionality

  6. Clean and user-friendly GUI using Java Swing

  7. MySQL database for storing user credentials and transaction data

Tech Stack :

  Frontend: Java Swing

  Backend: Java

  Database: MySQL

  IDE Used: IntelliJ IDEA 

